Always read `structure.md` before working in any folder.
Always keep `docs/` and every folder’s `structure.md` in sync with the codebase.
If you create, delete, rename, move, or reorganize any file/folder, update the affected `structure.md` files.
If the change affects a feature or the project architecture, update the relevant docs in `docs/`.
